<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="further-adj">further <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɜːðə(r)/    美 /'fɜːrðər/  </p>
<p>[far的比较级]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(距离、时间、程度上) 更远的；进一步的；更多的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>at the further end of the room 
在屋子的那一头</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have decided to take <strong>no further action</strong>.
我们决定不采取进一步行动。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My cousin left home to Australia for his further study last year.
我表弟去年离开家去澳大利亚深造。</p><footer>2010 山东书面表达改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Visit our website for <strong>further details / information</strong>.
欲知详情，请访问我们的网站。</p></div></div>